components.name: Data & Analytics || Analytics Data Platform - EOL

incident_updates.body: Update : Incident still ongoing, resolution is being processed and will take some time. We will get back to you as soon as a significant progress is visible.

Initial investigation indicates that block storage and volume snapshot products are not impacted.
A fix is currently being tested.
We'll be back shortly once the test has been validated and is being deployed.

Start time : 06/07/2022 09:00 UTC Service impact : We observe temporary 404 on GET method and 503 on PUT method, both due to misplaced objects. Ongoing actions : Our teams investigate to resolve the situation.

Estimated time to recovery : 1 hour(s)
